HEADWORD: Cockeye
<hw>Cock"eye`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>The socket in
the ball of a millstone, which sits on the cockhead.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

